tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE proteins (
    protein_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    protein_name STRING,
    expression_level FLOAT,
    study_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE ProteinExpressionStudies (
    study_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    study_name STRING,
    study_start_date DATE,
    study_end_date DATE,
    researcher_name STRING
);

CREATE TABLE ProteinExpressionData (
    data_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    study_id UUID REFERENCES ProteinExpressionStudies(study_id),
    protein_name STRING,
    expression_value FLOAT,
    sample_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE BiopharmaceuticalDevelopment (
    development_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    data_id UUID REFERENCES ProteinExpressionData(data_id),
    compound_name STRING,
    target_protein STRING,
    experimental_stage STRING,
    development_status STRING
);

CREATE TABLE Samples (
    sample_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    study_id UUID,
    protein_id UUID,
    sample_name VARCHAR(255),
    sample_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE StudyResults (
    result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    sample_id INT,
    gene_id INT,
    condition_id INT,
    result_description TEXT
);
